I would take an ass-kickin'

31:07.198 --> 31:10.201
just to make myself feel better,
but I have come to find out it's not.

31:10.368 --> 31:12.412
-No, huh?
-The job did not hurt you

31:12.495 --> 31:14.122
for reopening the Suarez case.

31:14.205 --> 31:16.499
Just my turn to be
Black man in the basket.

31:16.666 --> 31:17.750
