-(SIGHS) No.

34:35.823 --> 34:37.283
This was me shootin' ourselves in the foot

34:37.450 --> 34:39.786
so them people don't think
they got the market cornered.

34:40.078 --> 34:41.162
Oh.

34:52.673 --> 34:55.384
Graham. Cancel the press conference.

35:05.436 --> 35:07.271
Yeah. Okay, thanks.

35:07.814 --> 35:11.025
